ng against corruption in november  the company received the outstanding sustainability report award  organized by the thai listed companies association the securities and exchange commission and thaipat institution as well as the csr recognition award  and the top corporate governance award  organized by the stock exchange of thailand in june  indorama ventures received the best polymer producers awards for europe  in the category of pet during the main conference of the european plastics converters eupc annual meeting in  indorama ventures is in the top  companies with good level of transparency in transparency internationals research on transparency in corporate reporting charitycsr activitiesedit in august  the company signed the memorandum of understanding mou with operation smile thailand to provide support for surgery on children with cleft lips and palates in the country referencesedit  a b indorama ventures the stock exchange of thailand    a b c background of the company indorama ventures    httpwwwindoramaventurescomenourcompanyourcompanyphp  indorama ventures financial highlights indorama ventures    a b overview indorama ventures    ivl annual report  pp   httpwwwbangkokpostcomprint  ‘global pet resin market report  edition’ httpwwwresearchandmarketscomresearchshztglobalpet  ‘indorama agrees to acquire  stake in bangkok polyester’  march  httpwwwpackaginggatewaycomnewsnewsindoramaagreestoacquirestakeinbangkokpolyester   indorama ventures’ board of directors indorama ventures    ivl major shareholders indorama ventures    set added new listed securities ivl pdf indorama ventures    board of the year and audit committee of the year award  indorama ventures    thai institute of directors association thai institute of directors association    forbes asia fab  year  forbes asia    cen’s global top  year  cen    cac certified companies pdf thai institute of directors association    thai chamber of commerce thai chamber of commerce    the joint foreign chambers